section.faq.block 
	.container 
		.faq-grid 
			.faq-grid__title 
				h2.faq__title.text-uppercase.mb-0.text-center.text-lg-left Faq
			.faq-grid__img
				img.img-rounded.faq__img(src="img/faq-img.jpg" alt="")
			.faq-grid__accordion
				.faq__accordion
					.accordion
						.accordion-item.card.card-primary-outline
							.accordion-item__header
								h3.h4.accordion-item__title What should I do while waiting for you to arrive? 
								button.accordion-item__btn.btn.btn-small.btn-transparent#accordion-btn-1(type="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-item-1") 
									span.sr-only Toggle cards
									svg.icon(width="16" height="16")
										use(href="#caret-down")
							.accordion-item__body#faq-item-1(role="region" aria-labelledby="accordion-btn-1")
								.h5 Don’t panic — we’ve done this thousands of times and you’re in good hands. Move valuables away from the affected area, open windows for airflow where safe, and avoid household fans as they can spread contaminants.
						.accordion-item.card.card-primary-outline
							.accordion-item__header
								h3.h4.accordion-item__title Do I need to leave my home during the work? 
								button.accordion-item__btn.btn.btn-small.btn-transparent#accordion-btn-2(type="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-item-2") 
									span.sr-only Toggle cards
									svg.icon(width="16" height="16")
										use(href="#caret-down")
							.accordion-item__body#faq-item-2(role="region" aria-labelledby="accordion-btn-2")
								.h5 In most cases, no. Our equipment runs quietly and safely while you go about your day. If you feel it's safer to temporarily relocate, just let us know so we can coordinate.
						.accordion-item.card.card-primary-outline
							.accordion-item__header
								h3.h4.accordion-item__title Can you prevent mould from developing? 
								button.accordion-item__btn.btn.btn-small.btn-transparent#accordion-btn-3(type="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-item-3") 
									span.sr-only Toggle cards
									svg.icon(width="16" height="16")
										use(href="#caret-down")
							.accordion-item__body#faq-item-3(role="region" aria-labelledby="accordion-btn-3")
								.h5 Yes — fast response is key. Mould can start within 24–48 hours of water damage. Our equipment is designed to bring moisture levels down before mould takes hold. If pre-existing spores are present, water damage accelerates their growth — which is why acting quickly matters.
						.accordion-item.card.card-primary-outline 
							.accordion-item__header
								h3.h4.accordion-item__title Will you speak to my insurance company for me? 
								button.accordion-item__btn.btn.btn-small.btn-transparent#accordion-btn-4(type="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-item-4") 
									span.sr-only Toggle cards
									svg.icon(width="16" height="16")
										use(href="#caret-down")
							.accordion-item__body#faq-item-4(role="region" aria-labelledby="accordion-btn-4")
								.h5 Whilst we handle insurance claims daily and know exactly what documentation insurers need, we cannot look after your claim on your behalf. We can provide detailed reports, photos, and moisture readings, and we're happy to share these directly with your insurer to make the process as stress-free as possible.
						.accordion-item.card.card-primary-outline
							.accordion-item__header
								h3.h4.accordion-item__title What if I am renting and do not own the property? 
								button.accordion-item__btn.btn.btn-small.btn-transparent#accordion-btn-5(type="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-item-5") 
									span.sr-only Toggle cards
									svg.icon(width="16" height="16")
										use(href="#caret-down")
							.accordion-item__body#faq-item-5(role="region" aria-labelledby="accordion-btn-5")
								.h5 We work with renters regularly. Simply let your landlord or property manager know about the damage, and we can coordinate directly with them or their insurer. Your contents may be covered under your renters insurance—we can help document any personal items affected.
						.accordion-item.card.card-primary-outline
							.accordion-item__header
								h3.h4.accordion-item__title How long does the process take to dry out?
								button.accordion-item__btn.btn.btn-small.btn-transparent#accordion-btn-6(type="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-item-6") 
									span.sr-only Toggle cards
									svg.icon(width="16" height="16")
										use(href="#caret-down")
							.accordion-item__body#faq-item-6(role="region" aria-labelledby="accordion-btn-6")
								.h5 Every type of situation is different. It depends on how much water has been absorbed by the porous materials inside your home. 
						.accordion-item.card.card-primary-outline
							.accordion-item__header
								h3.h4.accordion-item__title Are you available 24/7 including public holidays?
								button.accordion-item__btn.btn.btn-small.btn-transparent#accordion-btn-7(type="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-item-7")
									span.sr-only Toggle cards
									svg.icon(width="16" height="16")
										use(href="#caret-down")
							.accordion-item__body#faq-item-7(role="region" aria-labelledby="accordion-btn-7")
								.h5 Yes, water damage doesn't wait and neither do we. Our team is available around the clock, 365 days a year—including Christmas, Easter, and every public holiday. When you ask for help, we will dispatch a team immediately.
			.faq-grid__btn
				.faq__btn.text-center.text-lg-left
					+btn('btn btn-primary btn-rounded btn-large', 'SEND HELP NOW')